  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "The requirement to call dbconfigs.WithCredentials is bug prone and not sustainable.\r\n\r\nInstead, I propose that functions like dbconfigs.AppWithDB, etc call this internally. The additional requirement of this refactor is that we do not store the returned values from these functions anywhere. They need to be fetched on every use to make sure that the newest credentials are used.",
